prayers-salat-nafilah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-6Xf","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":3961,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/01\/oversleeps-misses-forgets-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":26737,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Prayer: If someone oversleeps and misses prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Qatadah reported: It was mentioned to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, that some of them missed the prayer while they slept and the Prophet said, \u201cIt is not neglectful if missed (unintentionally) because of sleep. Verily, it is only neglectful if missed while awake. If one\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37547,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/16\/abandons-salah\/","url_meta":{"origin":26737,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Whoever abandons the prayer commits unbelief","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 16, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Buraydah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe covenant between us and them is the prayer, so whoever abandons it has committed unbelief.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2621 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u0628\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0647\u0652\u062f\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12949,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/18\/prayer-4-before-asr\/","url_meta":{"origin":26737,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sunan: Four raka&#8217;at before &#8216;Asr recommended","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"May Allah have mercy on a person who prays four cycles before afternoon prayer.\" Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 430 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u062d\u0650\u0645\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0627\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0623\u064b \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37597,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/23\/imams-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":26737,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jama\u2019ah: Imams should supplicate for their congregants too","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 23, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Thawban reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe one who leads others in prayer should not supplicate only for himself to the exclusion of them. If he does so, he has betrayed them.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 357 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12945,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/18\/sunan-prayer-before-after-dhuhur\/","url_meta":{"origin":26737,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: The Prophet prays before or after","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: If the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, could not pray four cycles before noon prayer, he would pray them afterwards. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 426 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0644\u064e\u0645\u0652 \u064a\u064f\u0635\u064e\u0644\u0650\u0651 \u0623\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0639\u064b\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u0628\u0652\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0638\u064f\u0651\u0647\u0652\u0631\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0647\u064f\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","contex